Sub Replace   '  word replace    remove   ","    ":"    .....etc

     Loop:

       m=text.GetIndexOf(RPDum,RPW)

         If m=0 Then

            Goto end1

         endif 

       RPDum=Text.GetSubText(RPDum,1,m-1)+Text.GetSubTextToEnd(RPDum,m+1)

     Goto loop 

     end1:  

Endsub      

  


